{"tid":682334,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港仲有好多好好既人架","createTime":"2018-05-28T19:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T06:37:34.000Z","uid":159647,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cd053b9abb5ded438478cb673d7027a22a53fdb5","tid":682334,"uid":159647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T19:38:22.000Z","msg":"事情係咁既，我同fd係旺中行行下街跌咗部電話落地，但由於我同佢傾得開心過頭既關係完全冇發現。行咗幾步之後就有位好好心既男人叫靚女！靚女！跌咗部電話呀！叫多幾聲我地先發覺原來係我地跌咗部電話。<br />\n如果你係以上我所講既依位好心人既話，我同fd真係好多謝你~祝你同女朋友幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs雖然只係一件好少既事，但係都好值得表揚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好成日話香港冇好人呀！只係你地冇我咁好彩遇到。"},{"pid":"cc90a2261786d0e3fe6bbf5114f69f94afa954fd","tid":682334,"uid":101968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T20:20:07.000Z","msg":"變sp未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1decd8e073eadbb770d302e24a75e915b2c9f4","tid":682334,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T21:33:54.000Z","msg":"咁有無好心人可以俾個閪我屌下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0361c9c4dfd595e0763ccf3bdb8ad2a79d15e69c","tid":682334,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T21:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e03de637c54873f6a5d7ba8fd5a27507d9984f7","tid":682334,"uid":125427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T21:45:07.000Z","msg":"靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83dd1c4c294f7291d4e4ef0a6e7d6f326d60875","tid":682334,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T22:50:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌"},{"pid":"bf84043e94cd3bc17541c7de98a9a6df48140a50","tid":682334,"uid":170044,"